  <source>Chulalongkorn University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research project is a study to immunology changes in critically ill patients with severe
      sepsis by using Endotoxin Activity Assay (EAA) combined with Polymyxin-B Hemoperfusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
